column2: Single-cell transcriptomics analysis of pancreatic primary tumor and metastatic biopsy tissues -

The single-cell RNA profiles of dissociated 10 pancreatic primary tumors and 6 metastatic biopsies were obtained using the 10x Genomics Chromium platform Overall design Tissues were dissciated using a tumor dissociation kit Miltenyi Biotec on a gentleMACSTM Dissociator Single cell RNA-sequencing was carried out using using the Chromium Single Cell Gene Expression Solution system v2 by 10x Genomics and an Illumina HiSeq4000 sequencer
